In this work, by exciting the copper dimer using deep-ultraviolet light, spectra are recorded in the vicinity of the \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
